section.def:
Chairman
                (主席) means the Chairman of the Council appointed
            under section 3(2)(a) or any other person when acting as Chairman;

contribution
                (分擔費) means the contribution assessed under
                section 16;

Council
                (職安局) means the Occupational Safety and Health
            Council established under section 3;

member
                (成員) means a member of the Council referred to in
                section 3(2) and any person when acting as a member;

penalty
                (罰款) means the penalty payable under section
                19(3);

paragraph.content:
lodges, produces, supplies or sends for the purposes of this Ordinance or
                    otherwise makes use for those purposes of any declaration or other document, or
                    record, which to his knowledge is false in a material particular;

in keeping or maintaining any record for the purposes of this Ordinance
                    makes an entry which to his knowledge is false in a in a material particular;
                    or
